<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >AVP International's Global Learning Award</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="283fb3a4-b8c3-49dc-a38e-737399290a77" >

    <p>The AVP International's Global Learning Award recognizes an individual or team (faculty or staff) who have made significant contributions to Global Learning at Ryerson. The recognized activity or leadership can take place either on campus or abroad.</p> 
<p>Individual recipients receive a certificate and a one-time monetary award of $2,000 (subject to applicable deductions). Team recipients (a group of two to ten individuals) receive individual certificates and a total one-time monetary award of $3,000 (subject to applicable deductions) to be shared equally among members.</p> 
<p><strong>Key criteria:&nbsp;Service, leadership, and innovation</strong></p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#283fb3a4-b8c3-49dc-a38e-737399290a77");});</script></div>

				

				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="81fddcd1-56b9-4782-855b-895bf1bb2978" >

    <h2>Nomination guidelines</h2>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#81fddcd1-56b9-4782-855b-895bf1bb2978");});</script></div>

				

				
				<div class="resAccordion section">
























 


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <div class="panel-group accordion background-hidden" id="a69b6dc9-4cbc-40e3-94ca-b0e24ad76a2d" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
			
				<div class="resAccordionControl" role="group" aria-label="Accordion Actions">
					<button class="resAccordionOpenAll">Open All</button> <button class="resAccordionCloseAll">Close All</button>
				</div>
				<script type="text/javascript">$(document).ready(function(){ initResAccordionControl("a69b6dc9-4cbc-40e3-94ca-b0e24ad76a2d", false); });</script>
			
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1568753540726-eligibility-and-obligations" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1568753540726-eligibility-and-obligations" aria-controls="accordion-content-1568753540726-eligibility-and-obligations" aria-expanded="false">
                            Eligibility and obligations
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1568753540726-eligibility-and-obligations" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1568753540726-eligibility-and-obligations">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1568753540726 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="0748b724-aa75-4720-8d98-1fb912367439" >

    <h4><strong>Who can be nominated?</strong></h4> 
<ul> 
 <li>Ryerson faculty and staff (i.e. Senior Administrator or Director, MAC, CUPE 233, CUPE 3904, or OPSEU), with at least one year of service, employed on a career or term basis.
  <ul> 
   <li>Note: Individuals who have Global Learning-related responsibilities are included for consideration; however, it is understood that nominees’ contributions that go above and beyond their work responsibilities will be considered.</li> 
  </ul> </li> 
 <li>Nominations are only valid for the year in which they are submitted and must be based on achievements within the past year.</li> 
 <li>Recipients of this award may not receive the same award for the following two academic years.</li> 
</ul> 
<h4><strong>Team nominations:</strong></h4> 
<ul> 
 <li>Teams must have between two and ten individuals. Please contact the award administrator if your team has more than ten individuals.&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>A nominated team member is defined as someone who has made a significant contribution toward a project or initiative.&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>Submit the nomination under the team lead’s name. If there is no team lead, select one team member’s name.</li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#0748b724-aa75-4720-8d98-1fb912367439");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1568753546949-who-can-submit-a-nomination-" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#" href="#accordion-content-1568753546949-who-can-submit-a-nomination-" aria-controls="accordion-content-1568753546949-who-can-submit-a-nomination-" aria-expanded="false">
                            Who can submit a nomination?
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1568753546949-who-can-submit-a-nomination-" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1568753546949-who-can-submit-a-nomination-">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1568753546949 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="0b7e45db-0cb5-4c4a-b080-1ee1e91dbda4" >

